Shutter Release-Lymbyc Systym']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fprocessed-spirits%252Fid338820523%253Fi%253D338820762%2526uo%253D6%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Shutter Release-Lymbyc Systym']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/06/the-longed-for-season.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/longedforseason.jpg" alt="The Longed-For Season / When the Clouds" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/06/the-longed-for-season.php">The Longed-For Season<br />When the Clouds</a></h4><p>エレクトロニカの雰囲気も持つ作品です。シンプルで同じフレーズを繰り返すギターを聴き続けていると心地よく眠れるでしょう。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B003BBI5DO?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B003BBI5DO" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'The Longed-For Season-When the Clouds']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fthe-house-of-sleep%252Fid367130960%253Fi%253D367132555%2526uo%253D6%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'The Longed-For Season-When the Clouds']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/06/tanknology.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/tanlnology.jpg" alt="Tanknology / That Fucking Tank" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/06/tanknology.php">Tanknology<br />That Fucking Tank</a></h4><p>勢いのあるロックサウンド。オルタナティブロックのような乱暴な雰囲気がとてもかっこいい1枚です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B003BBI5DO?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B003BBI5DO" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Tanknology-That Fucking Tank']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fludwig-ii-of-bavaria%252Fid315571821%253Fi%253D315571920%2526uo%253D6%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Tanknology-That Fucking Tank']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/06/in-a-safe-place.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/inasafepiece.jpg" alt="In a Safe Place / The Album Leaf" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/06/in-a-safe-place.php">In a Safe Place<br />The Album Leaf</a></h4><p>楽曲が非常にシンプルなので美しいエレピやアコースティックギターの響きがダイレクトに脳に響いてきます。何度でも繰り返し聴きたい1枚。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B0031YSORS?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B0031YSORS" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'In a Safe Place-The Album Leaf']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fthule%252Fid15405970%253Fi%253D15405950%2526uo%253D6%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'In a Safe Place-The Album Leaf']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/06/aufgang.p